rows.label: campfev11_140_150_msg0001
rows.name:
Laura-sama, your mother
has settled down in a place
called Torigo Village.

rows.label: campfev11_140_150_msg0003
rows.name:
That's right. A regular ferry
leaves from Yajika Harbor.

rows.label: campfev11_140_150_msg0004
rows.name:
Come on, no time to waste.
Let's head for Gula.

rows.label: campfev11_140_150_msg0005
rows.name: Are you really coming with us?

rows.label: campfev11_140_150_msg0006
rows.name: A man is only as good as his word.

rows.label: campfev11_140_150_msg0007
rows.name:
I'm worried about my mom, but is
this really the right thing to do?
